A state of look near
====================================
If you are able to look the state of any one, you automatically connect/interact with them smoothly/naturally. You never realize about them but you realization perceive towards
their state.
None of the states of any object exists but for observation we only stop on particular state of energy/object. ie. you know every state of object is for just a moment till it is in your
observation.
In fact the state of every things also existed in the form of stream only.

If you are not able to look the state of objects/humans, then your perception not perceive towards the state of object but your perception perceive towards the object directly.
If you look the object/human directly it is obvious the object/humans looks different and hence your perception move in next zone ie relativity.

When your perception move in state of relativity, a explosion happen in your perception to relate/correlate in different direction based on your knowledge/foolishness gather in life.
After explosion happen in perception, perception move in next zone/state since its intensity become week due to distributed in many known/unknown direction.
At this state of perception your perception perceive in such a direction that realize you are better at some stage and you are poor at some stage. The stage where it realize
better there you get a test of good feeling and where it realize poor there you get a test of competition.

At this state you observation not engage to observe but it engage in the TEST only.
If your observation is at this state you automatically look here and there since it get the test.

***If your observation gating test away from you, it never look near***
***We always get stuck when we look hear and there since we get some test****
If fact we not get stuck here and there but we get stuck in test since it gives instant energy.
This is nothing but the greedy approach toward absorb energy.

But if your observation are able to look the state of object/human, you are in such a state that realize state of every human/object is just for moment of observation 
and the existence of state exists till you observe ie the state of object/human not exists since  every state of object/human is under stream only.

Due to understanding of the state of object, your observation goes away form you for the purpose of light observation and not gating any test like relativity so your observation
not engage here and there. It will return back near you.

When your observation gating test in you/in your activities/in your streaming, then it will engage in you and stay near to you.
This is nothing but the state of look near.
At this state the intensity of observation is in higher state
that give more flexibility to look in light state of object.
 
***Due to a state look near, our energy get save and hence one feel nice during observation****

